34:03.742 --> 34:06.378 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH CIRINCIONE, President,
Ploughshares
Fund: One nuclear weapon on one
city would

34:06.411 --> 34:12.384 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
