35:52.784 --> 35:53.318 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GEN. MICHAEL HAYDEN: Sure.

35:53.351 --> 35:55.286 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Sure.

35:55.320 --> 35:58.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
