37:26.244 --> 37:33.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Frankly, Hari, I think American
safety, American
security -- put the privacy
argument aside,

37:33.384 --> 37:39.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
