encryption.

37:42.894 --> 37:46.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I recognize that makes the
life of the
FBI more difficult, may even
make the life

37:46.898 --> 37:48.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
