37:48.800 --> 37:50.635 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: OK.

37:50.668 --> 37:54.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Speaking of tools, you have said
that enhanced
interrogation techniques, what
most American

37:54.772 --> 37:59.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
