38:21.533 --> 38:24.769 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GEN. MICHAEL HAYDEN: Well, I
came to the agency
in '06, all right?

38:24.802 --> 38:29.874 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
