38:40.652 --> 38:42.453 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Some laws had changed, all
right?

38:42.487 --> 38:47.792 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I was fairly willing to pull
the program
back. But I wasn't judging what
my predecessors

38:47.825 --> 38:54.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
