38:56.267 --> 38:58.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: You might not
judge your
predecessors, but the American
people certainly

38:58.903 --> 39:00.772 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
