39:00.805 --> 39:05.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you felt like were you on
solid legal footing,
why do this -- why do this in
renditions,

39:05.710 --> 39:12.217 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
