39:17.789 --> 39:19.657 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GEN. MICHAEL HAYDEN: Well, what
I try to suggest
-- and actually point out in
some detail in

39:19.691 --> 39:24.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
