wrong one-legged

40:19.284 --> 40:19.917 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
guy.

40:19.951 --> 40:21.619 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GEN. MICHAEL HAYDEN: Right.

40:21.653 --> 40:23.388 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And you had an
after-action
to figure out what went wrong.
