intelligence
I have seen, that's not the
case.

40:41.172 --> 40:42.907 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GEN. MICHAEL HAYDEN: Yes.

40:42.940 --> 40:45.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But the irony
